Package: PairTrading
Type: Package
Title:classical pair trading based on cointegration in finance
Version: 1.1
Date: 2012-03-24
Author: Shinichi Takayanagi, Kohta Ishikawa
Maintainer: Shinichi Takayanagi<shinichi.takayanagi@gmail.com>, Kohta Ishikawa<quantumcorgi@gmail.com>
Description: This package gives classical trading strategy called "Pair trading" to you. you can easily specify pairs for trading and do back-test by this package. It's based on cointegration. Cointegration is a statistical feature of time series proposed by Engle and Granger.
License: BSD
LazyLoad: yes
Depends: R(>= 2.13.1), xts, tseries